WEBVTT

00:00:02.545 --> 00:00:03.705
Can we not be like this?

00:00:03.785 --> 00:00:05.545
Let's talk this through.

00:00:06.145 --> 00:00:08.185
I know loss could trigger you.

00:00:08.265 --> 00:00:09.745
I want you to move on.

00:00:10.345 --> 00:00:11.305
Yeah.

00:00:11.945 --> 00:00:13.225
Seon Jae is about to leave the country.

00:00:13.305 --> 00:00:15.425
- If we let him get away…
- Hey! Stop right there!

00:00:15.505 --> 00:00:17.065
We'll never know
who he's been supplying the drugs to.

00:00:22.105 --> 00:00:23.105
Hey, are you okay?

00:00:23.185 --> 00:00:24.625
Hey!

00:00:26.705 --> 00:00:28.905
Commander Don will probably call you in
for questioning soon.

00:00:28.985 --> 00:00:30.105
It's your gun.

00:00:30.185 --> 00:00:31.745
I'll talk to the higher-ups myself.

00:00:31.825 --> 00:00:34.665
I'll tell them I was the one
who fired it, not you.

00:00:34.745 --> 00:00:36.305
Hand over your gun and badge.

00:00:36.385 --> 00:00:39.585
You're suspended indefinitely.

00:00:39.665 --> 00:00:43.625
The important thing for you now
is not getting fired.

00:00:44.305 --> 00:00:46.465
No matter what,

00:00:47.345 --> 00:00:49.025
I believe the two of us won't lose.

00:01:00.745 --> 00:01:02.185
Let me catch my breath.

00:01:07.185 --> 00:01:10.585
You've only been suspended for one day
and it's already like this.

00:01:10.665 --> 00:01:12.785
How are you supposed to handle the rest?

00:01:13.945 --> 00:01:16.825
When we get home, update me on the case.

00:01:17.705 --> 00:01:19.545
Even if I'm suspended,

00:01:19.625 --> 00:01:21.225
I'm still the team leader.

00:01:21.945 --> 00:01:22.985
Got it?

00:01:34.145 --> 00:01:37.425
This is why they say
you shouldn't work with your partner.

00:02:45.345 --> 00:02:47.345
Once you're done, leave right away.

00:02:47.425 --> 00:02:49.865
Oh, I can arrange a transfer for you.

00:02:49.945 --> 00:02:52.105
Or do you want to go back to Special Ops?

00:02:53.665 --> 00:02:55.305
Hold on, Commander Don.

00:02:55.825 --> 00:02:57.545
What is it, Captain?

00:03:01.745 --> 00:03:03.905
I'm sorry for taking so long to pack up.

00:03:05.185 --> 00:03:08.465
And thank you
for caring this much about me.

00:03:08.545 --> 00:03:11.185
As for the transfer,
I'll handle it myself.

00:03:11.785 --> 00:03:13.865
I wouldn't want to take up your time.

00:03:33.065 --> 00:03:34.385
From now on,

00:03:35.705 --> 00:03:38.585
the commander will probably
be watching the two of us more closely.

00:03:39.825 --> 00:03:41.465
We may need to keep some distance.

00:03:46.185 --> 00:03:47.745
Do you know…

00:03:49.425 --> 00:03:51.065
how uneasy I feel

00:03:51.145 --> 00:03:53.905
knowing I can't be with you all the time?

00:03:58.225 --> 00:04:00.105
But if we really have to be apart,

00:04:09.225 --> 00:04:10.825
I want you to be safe.

00:04:15.185 --> 00:04:19.624
Think of it as some space,
so we have time to miss each other more.

00:04:22.505 --> 00:04:24.425
Then I'll go back to being your superior.

00:04:25.905 --> 00:04:27.225
This is an order.

00:04:28.025 --> 00:04:29.185
Not from your superior,

00:04:31.785 --> 00:04:33.585
but from your boyfriend.

00:04:40.065 --> 00:04:41.825
Roger that, Inspector Kamin.

00:04:43.065 --> 00:04:44.625
Captain Jade's boyfriend.

00:04:46.385 --> 00:04:48.705
Yes, Captain Jade.

00:04:49.705 --> 00:04:51.185
Inspector Kamin's boyfriend.

00:05:12.025 --> 00:05:14.185
Has the IT department still not
tracked down Champ and Cherreen?

00:05:15.065 --> 00:05:16.425
We've identified the license plate.

00:05:16.505 --> 00:05:18.625
We're tracing their route through CCTV.

00:05:18.705 --> 00:05:20.265
I need it faster, Lieutenant Prai.

00:05:20.345 --> 00:05:21.585
Yes.

00:05:22.545 --> 00:05:25.745
Based on the forensic team's analysis
of Seon Jae's phone,

00:05:25.825 --> 00:05:27.945
we've identified a meetup location.

00:05:28.665 --> 00:05:30.065
It's near Tonkla's dorm.

00:05:31.465 --> 00:05:32.905
I'll check it out myself.

00:05:35.225 --> 00:05:36.185
I don't get it.

00:05:36.985 --> 00:05:39.625
How did the killer know
who picked truth or dare?

00:05:40.985 --> 00:05:44.345
And if they chose dare,
how did he know who to kill?

00:05:47.945 --> 00:05:50.105
I think the answers
to both Seon Jae and the killer

00:05:50.185 --> 00:05:52.265
are in Tonkla's room.

00:06:29.305 --> 00:06:32.505
You didn't tell anyone
that I'm investigating too, right?

00:06:35.585 --> 00:06:36.745
I didn't.

00:06:36.825 --> 00:06:38.705
Not even the team knows.

00:06:41.665 --> 00:06:42.785
Which room do you think it is?

00:06:43.745 --> 00:06:45.345
Should we check upstairs first?

00:06:46.585 --> 00:06:47.505
Let's go.

00:06:48.225 --> 00:06:49.145
Hello.

00:06:50.985 --> 00:06:52.505
Can I help you?

00:06:54.305 --> 00:06:58.305
We'd like to ask about
the tenant of the room here.

00:06:59.065 --> 00:07:01.585
What is this place used for?

00:07:01.665 --> 00:07:06.745
I'm not sure, but I think
it's rented as a storage space.

00:07:06.825 --> 00:07:08.985
Are you two here about something?

00:07:22.305 --> 00:07:24.745
We're officers
from the Investigation Unit.

00:07:25.625 --> 00:07:28.745
We have a few questions
about the tenant here.

00:07:29.425 --> 00:07:31.065
You two are police officers?

00:07:32.545 --> 00:07:34.105
Yes.

00:07:34.185 --> 00:07:38.505
Is the tenant a foreigner?

00:07:38.585 --> 00:07:40.785
Oh, no.

00:07:40.865 --> 00:07:43.105
Then what's the tenant's name?

00:07:43.185 --> 00:07:45.505
The tenant of that room is

00:07:45.585 --> 00:07:49.385
Mr. Yotsapon Cheewa-acha.

00:07:49.465 --> 00:07:51.305
He seems like a businessman.

00:07:51.385 --> 00:07:54.785
Every now and then,
cars come by to drop things off.

00:07:55.825 --> 00:07:56.985
I see.

00:07:58.225 --> 00:07:59.985
So the items are moved in batches?

00:08:33.625 --> 00:08:35.105
What are you doing, Inspector?

00:08:41.625 --> 00:08:44.065
Hey, Inspector!

00:08:44.144 --> 00:08:46.305
We don't have a warrant yet.

00:08:46.905 --> 00:08:48.105
Hey.

00:08:51.585 --> 00:08:53.945
After working here for a while,

00:08:54.025 --> 00:08:58.065
I've learned that bending the rules
is sometimes necessary

00:08:58.705 --> 00:09:00.545
to solve a case faster.

00:09:10.705 --> 00:09:11.785
Hey.

00:09:13.825 --> 00:09:15.105
Got it?

00:09:25.545 --> 00:09:26.905
That's right.

00:09:27.865 --> 00:09:31.145
Please look into Mr. Yotsapon Cheewa-acha

00:09:32.025 --> 00:09:33.065
and request a search warrant.

00:09:35.465 --> 00:09:37.185
It's the hospital where Dr. Puth works.

00:09:40.785 --> 00:09:43.825
Please expedite the warrant
and notify forensics to come immediately.

00:09:44.665 --> 00:09:46.265
Please take care of it.

00:09:48.785 --> 00:09:51.745
They've been smuggling chemical substances
out of the hospital

00:09:51.825 --> 00:09:53.505
and exchanging them here.

00:09:56.745 --> 00:09:59.465
This case involves Seon Jae
and the drug dealers.

00:10:00.745 --> 00:10:02.705
I'll contact Nicoli.

00:10:02.785 --> 00:10:04.545
Maybe Special Investigation can help.

00:10:12.025 --> 00:10:13.225
Dr. Puth?

00:10:36.545 --> 00:10:38.265
Tonkla's room.

00:10:43.465 --> 00:10:45.345
Why would they choose to store drugs here?

00:10:58.425 --> 00:10:59.785
Kamin.

00:11:14.905 --> 00:11:16.225
Where did you get my photo?

00:11:16.825 --> 00:11:18.665
I have my own people.

00:11:18.745 --> 00:11:20.945
I had them do it.

00:11:21.025 --> 00:11:23.025
Turn it around.

00:11:30.705 --> 00:11:31.785
Jade's.

00:11:31.865 --> 00:11:33.705
I don't mean the badge.

00:11:34.625 --> 00:11:35.945
I mean you.

00:11:36.025 --> 00:11:37.105
You belong to me.

00:11:39.625 --> 00:11:41.785
Thank you, Captain.

00:11:42.705 --> 00:11:44.825
Call me "Jade," not Captain.

00:11:45.505 --> 00:11:46.945
You're not my boss anymore.

00:11:47.545 --> 00:11:48.825
Call me by my nickname already.

00:11:48.905 --> 00:11:51.505
You don't have a badge or a gun now.

00:11:52.545 --> 00:11:54.665
This will make things easier for work.

00:12:07.185 --> 00:12:08.785
What are you doing?

00:12:13.945 --> 00:12:16.705
JADE'S

00:12:26.985 --> 00:12:31.425
Then let me put it on for you.

00:12:52.505 --> 00:12:53.745
That was smooth.

00:12:54.465 --> 00:12:57.905
So do you like it, Jade?

00:13:20.025 --> 00:13:22.225
We're still trying to contact
the tenant's relatives,

00:13:22.305 --> 00:13:24.945
so the belongings
haven't been cleared yet.

00:13:25.025 --> 00:13:27.185
Feel free to look around.

00:13:27.985 --> 00:13:29.305
Thank you.

00:13:31.065 --> 00:13:33.665
What? The lights are still faulty?

00:13:33.745 --> 00:13:36.345
I'll call a technician.

00:13:37.385 --> 00:13:38.785
Thanks.

00:14:32.465 --> 00:14:33.945
Hello, doctor.

00:14:37.905 --> 00:14:39.345
Resigned?

00:14:40.785 --> 00:14:42.545
Please check Bell's condo for me.

00:14:42.625 --> 00:14:45.625
Has any electrician or anyone else
been there in the past two weeks?

00:14:46.425 --> 00:14:48.145
Please take care of it.

00:14:48.225 --> 00:14:50.705
I think we need backup
from Special Investigation.

00:14:50.785 --> 00:14:52.945
I've already contacted Yu and Lee.

00:14:55.705 --> 00:14:57.865
Hello, Inspector. Hello, Captain.

00:14:58.545 --> 00:15:00.825
What do you mean? Dr. Puth resigned?

00:15:01.505 --> 00:15:04.905
Yes. I couldn't reach him at all.
He didn't answer my call.

00:15:05.545 --> 00:15:07.585
So I came to the hospital myself.

00:15:07.665 --> 00:15:09.625
That's when I found out he'd resigned.

00:15:11.425 --> 00:15:12.785
At a time like this?

00:15:14.265 --> 00:15:17.625
Yes, but there's something
even more shocking.

00:15:21.545 --> 00:15:23.945
MORGUE

00:15:26.825 --> 00:15:29.305
I haven't received any request
to transfer the body yet.

00:15:29.385 --> 00:15:32.585
When the doctor asked to see the body,
I checked it myself.

00:15:37.825 --> 00:15:38.945
Yes.

00:15:39.025 --> 00:15:42.225
After they took me to see the body,
that is exactly what I saw.

00:15:45.505 --> 00:15:47.425
But once I realized this,

00:15:47.505 --> 00:15:50.785
I immediately sent Puifai's name
to Medical Records to be checked.

00:15:50.865 --> 00:15:55.785
I found that she had a history
of treatment for depression here.

00:15:57.025 --> 00:15:58.985
There is also a record of her body
being brought in

00:15:59.065 --> 00:16:01.505
with Dr. Puth listed
as the attending physician.

00:16:02.505 --> 00:16:04.305
Could I have the documents, please?

00:16:06.265 --> 00:16:07.145
Here you are.

00:16:09.025 --> 00:16:12.665
{\an8}What's strange is that
it wasn't Dr. Puth's shift that day.

00:16:12.745 --> 00:16:15.745
He shouldn't have arrived
at the scene that quickly.

00:16:17.865 --> 00:16:19.945
{\an8}BODY INTAKE RECORD

00:16:20.025 --> 00:16:24.065
{\an8}RECEIVING OFFICER:
MR. YOTSAPON CHEEWA-ACHA

00:16:24.625 --> 00:16:26.265
Then what's the tenant's name?

00:16:26.345 --> 00:16:29.145
Mr.Yotsapon Cheewa-acha.

00:16:29.225 --> 00:16:30.865
That's Dr. Puth's real name.

00:16:32.865 --> 00:16:35.345
Yotsapon Cheewa-acha.

00:16:47.585 --> 00:16:49.065
Please, come in.

00:16:54.705 --> 00:16:58.225
Dr. Puth is usually quiet
and keeps to himself.

00:16:58.305 --> 00:16:59.425
He doesn't talk to people much.

00:16:59.505 --> 00:17:01.545
But I noticed that
after he started dating someone,

00:17:01.625 --> 00:17:03.625
he seemed much brighter.

00:17:04.424 --> 00:17:06.345
- He has a partner?
- Yes.

00:17:07.265 --> 00:17:10.464
I think it's this person in the photo,
if I'm not mistaken.

00:17:16.545 --> 00:17:18.305
Excuse me, doctor.

00:17:18.385 --> 00:17:20.985
Call me once you're done.

00:17:21.065 --> 00:17:22.944
Of course. Thank you so much.

00:17:27.785 --> 00:17:29.625
Does this mean

00:17:29.705 --> 00:17:31.905
Dr. Puth really killed those students?

00:17:34.225 --> 00:17:36.465
It's too early to conclude that,

00:17:37.425 --> 00:17:39.825
but if we're talking about motive,

00:17:39.905 --> 00:17:40.865
it's possible.

00:17:40.945 --> 00:17:44.185
I think Dr. Puth was trying
to avenge Puifai

00:17:45.665 --> 00:17:47.585
because they were dating
behind Champ's back.

00:17:48.305 --> 00:17:51.025
When he learned she had died,
he wanted revenge.

00:17:52.425 --> 00:17:54.465
And the reason he got involved
in this case

00:17:55.265 --> 00:17:56.665
was to get close to the police.

00:17:57.505 --> 00:17:59.665
But taking the body with him?

00:18:00.385 --> 00:18:02.265
Don't you think
that's a bit too psychotic?

00:18:14.785 --> 00:18:16.145
REBAR, DRUGGED WOMEN, ATTEMPTED RAPE

00:18:20.505 --> 00:18:22.025
ACID ATTACK, TOOK A FRIEND FOR AN ABORTION

00:18:28.945 --> 00:18:31.145
I think this goes beyond just psychotic.

00:18:32.905 --> 00:18:34.145
STOLE A CUSTOMER'S CAR, HIT AN ELDERLY MAN

00:18:45.505 --> 00:18:47.305
Excuse me.

00:18:47.385 --> 00:18:48.585
Yes.

00:18:49.985 --> 00:18:52.225
Oh, Dr. Puth isn't here?

00:18:53.185 --> 00:18:55.545
No, he isn't. Is something wrong?

00:18:55.625 --> 00:18:58.585
I need the doctor to sign
some lab documents.

00:19:00.425 --> 00:19:01.945
Lab documents?

00:19:02.825 --> 00:19:03.825
May I see them?

00:19:06.665 --> 00:19:08.665
I'm a police officer.

00:19:09.545 --> 00:19:10.825
Yes.

00:19:11.585 --> 00:19:12.825
Thank you.

00:19:17.305 --> 00:19:21.185
Is Dr. Puth in charge
of the chemical stock?

00:19:21.265 --> 00:19:23.105
Yes.

00:19:28.185 --> 00:19:29.705
It's the hospital where Dr. Puth works.

00:19:39.545 --> 00:19:42.305
Please make sure all the footage
is properly collected.

00:19:46.185 --> 00:19:49.065
Does this mean the culprit
is the forensic pathologist

00:19:49.665 --> 00:19:51.985
who handled the first victim's case?

00:19:52.585 --> 00:19:54.985
Mr. Puth, please rush the results for me.

00:19:55.585 --> 00:19:57.025
Of course, Inspector.

00:20:00.505 --> 00:20:01.505
Hello, doctor.

00:20:03.225 --> 00:20:04.385
Hello.

00:20:04.465 --> 00:20:07.785
We're sorry for the delay, Inspector.

00:20:07.865 --> 00:20:09.225
On top of that,

00:20:09.305 --> 00:20:11.825
there's the issue of smuggling
chemical substances to produce drugs.

00:20:12.945 --> 00:20:14.705
Everything seems to line up.

00:20:14.785 --> 00:20:16.585
This explains where Seon Jae
got the drugs.

00:20:17.745 --> 00:20:21.865
Just chemicals from labs and the hospital…

00:20:22.945 --> 00:20:25.105
Can they really produce drugs
on that scale?

00:20:25.185 --> 00:20:28.465
Puth may be one of the suppliers
providing the chemicals.

00:20:28.545 --> 00:20:31.785
But I believe there are others
doing the same thing as well.

00:20:31.865 --> 00:20:34.425
Once the search warrant is issued,

00:20:34.505 --> 00:20:39.025
I'll inspect the warehouse
where Puth met Seon Jae.

00:20:39.105 --> 00:20:40.345
Please take care of it.

00:20:40.425 --> 00:20:41.665
Yes.

00:20:55.145 --> 00:20:57.585
Police have discovered that
socialite Champ, the son of MP Ratana,

00:20:57.665 --> 00:20:59.865
was involved in drug trafficking
with Seon Jae,

00:20:59.945 --> 00:21:02.825
a major dealer
who was shot dead at the scene.

00:21:02.905 --> 00:21:04.385
This may serve as evidence linking Champ

00:21:04.465 --> 00:21:06.265
to the murder of
a fellow university student,

00:21:06.345 --> 00:21:09.145
a case in which he is already a suspect.

00:21:10.985 --> 00:21:12.505
Damn, Champ.

00:21:23.905 --> 00:21:25.345
- Hello.
- Hello.

00:21:30.745 --> 00:21:32.385
You're not my regular doctor.

00:21:32.465 --> 00:21:35.105
Your regular doctor is tied up in surgery.

00:21:35.185 --> 00:21:37.345
I'm here to update you on your condition
and go over the details.

00:21:37.425 --> 00:21:39.985
At this point,
your condition appears stable.

00:21:40.065 --> 00:21:43.345
The CT scan shows no issues
and the wound is healing well.

00:21:43.425 --> 00:21:46.065
There shouldn't be any complications.
You should be able to go home tomorrow.

00:21:46.945 --> 00:21:49.425
- So I can go home?
- Yes.

00:21:49.505 --> 00:21:51.865
But if you're exposed
to too much sun or rain,

00:21:52.865 --> 00:21:54.865
your condition could worsen.

00:21:57.065 --> 00:21:58.265
All right.

00:21:58.345 --> 00:21:59.785
Thank you very much.

00:22:17.945 --> 00:22:19.905
Why are you watching me so closely?

00:22:48.145 --> 00:22:50.425
How is it, Ken? Did you get anything?

00:22:51.905 --> 00:22:56.545
I got the files from IT and checked
Bell's condo, just like you asked.

00:22:56.625 --> 00:22:58.225
An electrician really did come.

00:22:58.305 --> 00:23:00.505
We also found a hidden camera,
the same model as in Tonkla's room,

00:23:00.585 --> 00:23:02.185
inside a doll in Bell's room.

00:23:09.585 --> 00:23:13.265
EVIDENCE

00:23:55.545 --> 00:24:00.185
The IT team and I took the forensics team
to inspect Puth's warehouse,

00:24:00.265 --> 00:24:02.465
so we took this camera in
to examine it as well.

00:24:02.545 --> 00:24:05.745
We found that the signal connects directly
to that location.

00:24:07.105 --> 00:24:09.745
He must have been lying low
near every victim.

00:24:09.825 --> 00:24:11.905
He had that much money

00:24:11.985 --> 00:24:13.745
because he was dealing drugs
with Seon Jae.

00:24:13.825 --> 00:24:16.625
Then why didn't the killer
remove the camera?

00:24:18.105 --> 00:24:20.225
I guess he wanted to track our movements,

00:24:20.305 --> 00:24:22.425
so he could always stay one step ahead.

00:24:23.625 --> 00:24:26.025
He probably thought we couldn't stop him.

00:24:26.825 --> 00:24:28.625
The Department of Highways
hasn't approved the request yet.

00:24:28.705 --> 00:24:32.225
Cherreen, Champ, and Puth
are still missing.

00:24:34.225 --> 00:24:35.865
So what do we do now?

00:24:44.545 --> 00:24:45.825
Hello, Captain.

00:24:45.905 --> 00:24:47.545
We're sorry to keep you waiting.

00:24:51.545 --> 00:24:53.025
{\an8}NOT FOUND

00:25:00.345 --> 00:25:01.265
Thanks.

00:25:03.585 --> 00:25:04.985
CHATUCHAK

00:25:06.985 --> 00:25:09.185
NAVANAKORN INDUSTRIAL ZONE, PATHUM THANI

00:25:21.385 --> 00:25:23.185
What's up, Jade?

00:25:26.185 --> 00:25:27.585
Jade.

00:25:28.385 --> 00:25:29.305
What's going on?

00:25:30.545 --> 00:25:31.705
I miss you.

00:25:32.745 --> 00:25:37.825
Wow, did you call me just to say that?

00:25:38.985 --> 00:25:42.065
I just wanted to hear your voice.
Do I need a reason?

00:25:42.665 --> 00:25:45.465
You heard it now. Can I hang up?

00:25:45.545 --> 00:25:47.385
Hey, wait.

00:25:48.945 --> 00:25:51.825
I already sent the Special Ops.

00:25:51.905 --> 00:25:53.865
They should be there by now.
Have they arrived?

00:25:54.985 --> 00:25:56.345
They have.

00:25:56.425 --> 00:25:57.545
Thank you.

00:25:57.625 --> 00:25:58.585
Don't worry.

00:25:59.185 --> 00:26:02.425
Think of them as my stand-ins.

00:26:03.985 --> 00:26:05.825
No one can replace you.

00:26:08.145 --> 00:26:11.185
I really wish you were here,
talking to me up close,

00:26:12.145 --> 00:26:13.865
so I could steal a kiss.

00:26:17.545 --> 00:26:20.465
By the way, I already sent you
some encouragement.

00:26:20.545 --> 00:26:22.225
It should've arrived.

00:26:23.065 --> 00:26:24.385
What?

00:26:26.825 --> 00:26:29.145
Hello. Captain Jade's order.

00:26:29.225 --> 00:26:30.465
Yes.

00:26:31.585 --> 00:26:34.225
The customer asked me to say,

00:26:35.905 --> 00:26:38.025
“It's encouragement from your boyfriend.”

00:26:45.705 --> 00:26:47.185
Share it with the Special Ops.

00:26:47.785 --> 00:26:52.745
If that's all, I'll go check on Jay
and update you.

00:26:54.585 --> 00:26:55.825
All right.

00:26:57.105 --> 00:26:58.465
Thanks, Min.

00:26:58.545 --> 00:26:59.465
No problem,

00:26:59.545 --> 00:27:02.065
Jade, Kamin's boyfriend.

00:27:04.425 --> 00:27:06.345
All right. Love you.

00:27:12.545 --> 00:27:13.425
Everyone, come on.

00:27:14.785 --> 00:27:18.265
Let's eat first. Take a break.

00:27:28.985 --> 00:27:30.305
Whoa.

00:27:30.905 --> 00:27:36.505
I can't believe Captain Jade
changed you this much

00:27:36.585 --> 00:27:38.625
from the first day I met you.

00:27:40.425 --> 00:27:41.465
I changed?

00:27:42.945 --> 00:27:46.785
Inspector, have you ever walked around
smiling like this before?

00:27:47.625 --> 00:27:49.465
I'm really curious.

00:27:49.545 --> 00:27:54.105
What did Captain Jade do
to make you like this?

00:27:57.705 --> 00:27:59.625
Get back to work. Stop teasing.

00:27:59.705 --> 00:28:01.945
Gosh. Kicking me out already?

00:28:02.025 --> 00:28:03.945
All right then.

00:28:04.025 --> 00:28:05.385
I'm getting back to work.

00:28:05.465 --> 00:28:07.105
See you later.

00:28:07.185 --> 00:28:11.105
Wait, I'll get going, Inspector Kamin,

00:28:11.705 --> 00:28:12.665
Captain Jade's.

00:28:14.625 --> 00:28:15.905
See you.

00:28:35.705 --> 00:28:36.905
Jay.

00:28:48.465 --> 00:28:49.705
Jay.

00:28:50.545 --> 00:28:52.065
It's Kamin.

00:29:04.345 --> 00:29:05.665
Fuck!

00:29:09.945 --> 00:29:11.505
- Jay's gone?
- Yes.

00:29:11.585 --> 00:29:14.505
The officer was hit on the back
of the head and knocked unconscious.

00:29:14.585 --> 00:29:16.745
I'm checking the CCTV right now.

00:29:17.505 --> 00:29:18.985
Okay. I'm heading there now.

00:29:19.065 --> 00:29:20.025
No need.

00:29:20.105 --> 00:29:22.905
Even if you come,
there's nothing you can do.

00:29:22.985 --> 00:29:24.985
You're more useful staying where you are.

00:29:25.585 --> 00:29:27.985
Let Yuki and Lee help investigate
and track down leads.

00:29:28.065 --> 00:29:30.265
- But…
- Hey.

00:29:30.345 --> 00:29:33.545
I'll investigate as fast as I can
and update you on everything.

00:29:33.625 --> 00:29:34.705
Don't worry.

00:29:39.945 --> 00:29:42.625
Okay. I'm counting on you.

00:29:44.065 --> 00:29:45.225
Yes.

00:29:50.705 --> 00:29:53.345
Who was the last person
to enter Jay's room?

00:29:54.105 --> 00:29:56.705
That day, the regular doctor
was tied up with another case,

00:29:56.785 --> 00:29:58.825
so a substitute doctor had to come in.

00:30:10.385 --> 00:30:11.625
This one here?

00:30:12.705 --> 00:30:14.185
No.

00:30:14.265 --> 00:30:16.465
The substitute that day
was supposed to be a woman.

00:30:17.225 --> 00:30:20.065
And she never clocked in.

00:30:21.185 --> 00:30:23.345
Can you skip ahead a bit?

00:30:23.425 --> 00:30:24.305
Of course.

00:30:54.465 --> 00:30:55.345
Hello, Min.

00:30:56.305 --> 00:30:57.785
Jay's received the letter.

00:30:57.865 --> 00:31:00.505
But it looks like he went somewhere.

00:31:00.585 --> 00:31:01.465
Where are you going?

00:31:01.545 --> 00:31:02.625
To find Jay.

00:31:43.105 --> 00:31:44.665
I did it!

00:31:44.745 --> 00:31:46.145
I raped Puifai!

00:31:56.425 --> 00:31:57.625
Are you that damn horny?

00:31:57.705 --> 00:31:58.745
You're that damn horny, huh?

00:32:02.305 --> 00:32:03.385
Hey!

00:32:11.945 --> 00:32:12.825
Let me go!

00:32:12.905 --> 00:32:15.345
I already chose dare. I chose dare!

00:32:15.425 --> 00:32:16.545
- I chose Cherreen!
- Shut up!

00:32:34.785 --> 00:32:36.705
I sold my friend for money!

00:32:38.185 --> 00:32:39.905
Can you let me go now?

00:32:40.865 --> 00:32:42.505
What the hell are you doing?

00:32:46.025 --> 00:32:48.145
Didn't you tell me to handle Jay,

00:32:48.225 --> 00:32:50.225
dump the car, and then let me go?

00:32:53.865 --> 00:32:54.785
Hey!

00:33:23.905 --> 00:33:25.345
Hey, I found it.

00:33:31.105 --> 00:33:34.705
The car belonging to Mr. Chayamporn,
or Champ, headed toward Navanakorn.

00:33:34.785 --> 00:33:36.665
It left Bangkok

00:33:37.825 --> 00:33:41.105
and seems to have stopped at a house…

00:33:41.705 --> 00:33:43.145
right here.

00:33:46.305 --> 00:33:48.825
- Ken, prepare backup. We're moving in.
- Yes.

00:34:11.225 --> 00:34:13.385
You're the doctor
who examined Puifai's body, aren't you?

00:34:15.105 --> 00:34:16.105
Ding-dong.

00:34:38.025 --> 00:34:38.945
Choose.

00:34:39.545 --> 00:34:41.304
Who are you going to save?

00:34:43.905 --> 00:34:44.784
Champ?

00:34:51.705 --> 00:34:52.985
Or Cherreen?

00:34:56.585 --> 00:34:58.305
I'm heading to the abandoned farm now

00:34:59.025 --> 00:35:01.545
based on the GPS tracker
I put in Jay's bag.

00:35:07.425 --> 00:35:09.385
Wait for me. We go together.

00:35:09.465 --> 00:35:11.785
Jade, this isn't something we can wait on.

00:35:11.865 --> 00:35:14.985
I'm already on the road
that leads straight to Jay.

00:35:15.065 --> 00:35:17.145
I'll go first. You follow.

00:35:17.225 --> 00:35:19.105
You've been removed from the case.

00:35:19.185 --> 00:35:20.105
Wait for me.

00:35:20.745 --> 00:35:21.865
It's okay.

00:35:23.145 --> 00:35:25.945
No matter what,
I still have you by my side.

00:35:33.265 --> 00:35:36.385
I love you, Jade.

00:35:41.345 --> 00:35:42.865
Jade?

00:35:47.865 --> 00:35:48.745
Shit.

00:35:50.145 --> 00:35:51.465
My battery died.

00:35:52.145 --> 00:35:53.385
Kamin.

00:35:53.465 --> 00:35:55.345
Kamin!

00:35:55.425 --> 00:35:57.665
Lee, send me the location.

00:35:58.265 --> 00:35:59.105
Now.

00:35:59.185 --> 00:36:01.145
Ken, get backup.

00:36:01.225 --> 00:36:02.065
Yes.

00:36:03.825 --> 00:36:05.465
Sent.

00:36:06.345 --> 00:36:10.465
Captain, I found hydrofluoric substances
in Dr. Puth's warehouse.

00:36:10.545 --> 00:36:15.385
It's a black powder that can ignite
when exposed to oxygen.

00:36:15.465 --> 00:36:17.585
- Ignite?
- Yes.

00:36:17.665 --> 00:36:21.425
I'm afraid Dr. Puth is planning
to burn the house down

00:36:21.505 --> 00:36:23.865
or cause an explosion.

00:36:26.105 --> 00:36:26.985
Hello?

00:36:27.065 --> 00:36:28.145
Right?

00:36:40.905 --> 00:36:41.905
I'm not choosing!

00:36:41.985 --> 00:36:43.865
I'm not choosing anyone to die.

00:36:54.305 --> 00:36:55.785
Sweetheart.

00:36:56.705 --> 00:36:58.305
Your friend won't choose.

00:37:00.225 --> 00:37:01.985
What should we do?

00:37:04.665 --> 00:37:05.905
JADE'S

00:37:20.225 --> 00:37:21.545
What is it?

00:38:21.105 --> 00:38:23.385
If you weren't working beside me anymore,

00:38:24.785 --> 00:38:25.945
would you regret it?

00:38:29.945 --> 00:38:31.105
Of course I would.

00:38:31.745 --> 00:38:33.065
Wouldn't you?

00:38:37.225 --> 00:38:38.225
I wouldn't regret it.

00:38:39.345 --> 00:38:44.065
It's not because I don't want to see you.

00:38:45.665 --> 00:38:49.065
But it's because I believe that
no matter what happens,

00:38:49.145 --> 00:38:50.465
we'll always be together,

00:38:51.865 --> 00:38:54.185
waking up together every morning.

00:38:54.265 --> 00:38:56.465
Not as subordinate and superior,

00:38:57.985 --> 00:39:01.225
but as a couple.

00:39:33.545 --> 00:39:34.745
That's enough.

00:39:35.345 --> 00:39:36.985
Someone might see us.

00:39:37.585 --> 00:39:39.545
There's no one here

00:39:40.185 --> 00:39:42.065
but you and me.

00:39:43.585 --> 00:39:44.865
And even if there were,

00:39:46.105 --> 00:39:47.705
I wouldn't care.

00:39:49.865 --> 00:39:51.345
You're mine.

00:39:54.025 --> 00:39:55.545
I'm yours.

00:40:27.825 --> 00:40:29.865
So everything that's happened
was your doing?

00:40:29.945 --> 00:40:32.465
If you want to know that badly,
Jay, then choose.

00:40:32.545 --> 00:40:33.545
Truth or dare?

00:40:33.625 --> 00:40:35.785
- I won't choose!
- Then your game is over.

00:40:40.185 --> 00:40:41.225
This is the police.

00:40:41.305 --> 00:40:42.745
It's all over.

00:40:42.825 --> 00:40:46.065
But now, it's Champ's and Cherreen's turn.

00:40:46.145 --> 00:40:47.025
Kamin!

00:40:47.945 --> 00:40:49.065
Don't!

00:40:51.505 --> 00:40:53.065
We just closed a case this big.

00:40:53.665 --> 00:40:56.065
Let's go on a trip, babe.

00:40:57.345 --> 00:41:00.705
Thank you for coming into my life
and completing it.

00:41:00.785 --> 00:41:06.425
You showed me how good it feels
to have someone I love by my side.

00:41:06.505 --> 00:41:08.305
I love you,

00:41:08.385 --> 00:41:10.425
my Kamin.